Iteration 2 (i = 1):

    Current Number: 7

    Need: 2

    Is 2 in notebook? YES!

    The Return Line happens:

        numberWeNeed is 2.

        notebook[2] retrieves the value 0 (because we wrote that down in Iteration 1).

